@node "Cards" "Card Graphics"
If you think you can create some better graphics for the cards, go ahead and
try.  They need to be in ANSI/ASCII though...if you do get something better,
send me the ANSI file, and I'll try and include them in the game.  The
easiest way would be to UUEncode the graphics and @{"E-Mailing" link "Contact" 0} them to me.
@endnode
